# UI & UX (Compose Multiplatform)

## Layout & scrolling

- Use `ScreenLayout` tokens and `Modifier.screenContentArea()` + `screenListPadding()` for screen insets.
- Lists with bottom inputs: weighted `LazyColumn` + input bar (not a fixed scaffold bar that fights the keyboard).
- Apply `imePadding()` on scrollable content; Android activity uses `adjustResize` when adding text-heavy screens.

## Design system (current)

### Reuse first

- **Surfaces:** `FamilyLogisticsCardSurface`, `FamilyLogisticCard`, `NutritionFeatureHeader`, `FamilyLogisticsSectionHeader`, `JourneyBanner`
- **Chrome:** `NutritionScaffold`, `NapolitanBackground`, `WeekContextBanner`, `NutritionSyncStatusBanner`
- **Colors:** `SharedJourneyColors` only — no one-off hex in composables
- **Icons:** `AppIcons` only — no `Icons.Default` / platform icon imports in presentation
- **Layout tokens:** `ScreenLayout.horizontalPadding` (24dp), `sectionSpacing` (16dp), `FamilyLogisticsDesign` shapes

### Planned primitives (implement before wide screen refactors)

| Primitive | Purpose | Extract from |
|-----------|---------|--------------|
| `JourneyButton` (Primary / Secondary / Tertiary / Destructive) | Consistent action hierarchy + loading slot | `LoginScreen`, `HomeScreen` onboarding |
| `JourneyTextField` | Branded focus, shape, placeholder colors | `GroceryInputBar`, `NutritionAiAdviceScreen` |
| `JourneyIconButton` | 48×48dp minimum touch target | `GroceryItemRow`, `MealPlanDayCard` |
| `JourneyLoadingContent` | Spinner + optional message, brand color | Gates, `HomeLoadingContent` |
| `JourneyErrorContent` | Message + retry | `HomeErrorContent`, entry gates |
| `JourneyEmptyState` | Icon + title + body + optional CTAs | Unify `EmptyStateCard` + `MealPlanEmptyState` |

