## Icon semantics (`AppIcons.kt`)

**Rule:** Every `AppIcons` name must match user intent. Never alias unrelated icons.

### Broken aliases (fix in PR1 — ship blocker)

| Symbol | Current alias | User expectation | Used in |
|--------|---------------|------------------|---------|
| `MoreVert` | `Sparkles` | Overflow ⋮ menu | `HomeScreen`, `WeeklyMealPlanScreen` |
| `DateRange` | `Notifications` | Calendar / week range | `MealPlanEmptyState`, `NutritionHubScreen`, `WeeklyMealPlanScreen` |
| `KeyboardArrowDown` | `ChevronRight` | Expand section ↓ | `FamilyLogisticsDesign` collapsible |
| `KeyboardArrowUp` | `ChevronLeft` | Collapse section ↑ | same |
| `Check` | `CheckCircle` | Save / confirm (distinct from list check) | `GroceryItemRow` save |
| `Refresh` | `Sparkles` | Pull-to-refresh / reload | *(unused — add when needed)* |

### Correct custom vectors (keep)

`ChevronLeft`, `ChevronRight`, `ArrowBack`, `Add`, `Delete`, `Edit`, `CheckCircle`, `RadioButtonUnchecked`, `Restaurant`, `Explore`, `AccountBalance`, `Sparkles` (AI only)

### Dead aliases (implement real vector or delete)

`Favorite`, `Info`, `Person`, `Star` — no call sites today.

### Semantic rules

- `Sparkles` → AI-generated content only (`AiReadOnlyGroceryList`, `NutritionAiAdviceScreen`, meal-plan AI actions)
- `CheckCircle` / `RadioButtonUnchecked` → list completion state (grocery checkbox)
- `ChevronRight` → navigation affordance on cards (`FamilyLogisticCard`, `HomeHouseholdButton`)

