## Button hierarchy

| Variant | Material base | Color | When to use |
|---------|---------------|-------|-------------|
| **Primary** | `Button` | `MediterraneanTeal` fill (or theme primary) | Single main forward action per screen section |
| **Secondary** | `OutlinedButton` | Teal border | Alternate path, second CTA (e.g. meal plan “add manually”) |
| **Tertiary** | `TextButton` | `InkMuted` or teal | Cancel, dismiss dialog, low emphasis |
| **Destructive** | `TextButton` or `OutlinedButton` | `TerracottaOrange` | Sign out, delete account, clear AI data — always confirm in dialog when irreversible |

### Known inconsistencies to fix

| Location | Issue | Target |
|----------|-------|--------|
| `HomeScreen` onboarding create | `OutlinedButton` when pending invites, `Button` when none | Primary for create; pending invites are separate cards |
| `InviteEmailMismatchScreen` | Sign-out uses filled `Button` | Destructive `TextButton` or outlined destructive |
| Account sheet (`HomeScreen`) | Sign out / export / delete all `TextButton` | Destructive delete uses destructive variant |
| Dialogs | Mix of `Button` confirm + `TextButton` cancel | OK — document as standard dialog pattern |

### Loading on buttons

- Disable control while loading; show small `CircularProgressIndicator` inside button (see `LoginScreen`).
- Do not stack a full-screen spinner **and** button spinner for the same action.

