## Typography & color

### Defined roles (`AppTheme.kt`)

`displaySmall`, `headlineMedium`, `titleLarge`, `titleMedium`, `bodyLarge`, `bodyMedium`, `labelLarge`

### Roles used but undefined (add in foundation PR)

`titleSmall`, `bodySmall`, `labelSmall`, `labelMedium` — currently Material defaults.

### Line height

Body text (`bodyLarge`, `bodyMedium`, `bodySmall`): target **1.5×** font size for readability.

### Semantic colors (planned tokens)

| Token | Value / source | Use |
|-------|----------------|-----|
| Error (inline) | `TerracottaOrange` | Gates, form validation — **prefer over** `colorScheme.error` for brand consistency |
| Success | `MediterraneanTeal` | Email confirmation sent (`LoginScreen`) |
| On glass muted | TBD (contrast fix) | Placeholder, hints on `GlassWhite` surfaces |
| Focus border | `MediterraneanTeal` | `OutlinedTextField` focused state |
| Cursor | `TerracottaOrange` | Text field caret |

### Contrast watchlist

- `InkMuted` on `ParchmentWarm` — passes AA for body text
- `InkMuted` at reduced alpha on `GlassWhite` — **may fail** for `labelSmall` / hints — fix via `onGlassMuted` token

