## Touch targets

- **Minimum:** 48×48dp for all interactive controls (Material 3).
- **Token:** `FamilyLogisticsDesign.minTouchTarget` (add when implementing `JourneyIconButton`).
- **Compliant today:** `FeatureAccentIconButton` (48dp), grocery checkbox `IconButton`, swipe-to-dismiss row.
- **Non-compliant (fix in PR5+):** `GroceryItemRow` edit/save `IconButton`, `MealPlanDayCard` clear, `NutritionScaffold` back, `HomeScreen` overflow, week nav chevrons in `NutritionUxComponents`.

Use `Modifier.minimumInteractiveComponentSize()` or explicit `size(48.dp)` on `IconButton`.

