## UX state patterns

### Requirements (every primary flow)

| State | Pattern | Component (target) |
|-------|---------|-------------------|
| **Loading** | Centered spinner + localized message when >300ms | `JourneyLoadingContent` |
| **Error** | Inline or full-screen message + retry; snackbar for async | `JourneyErrorContent` / snackbar |
| **Empty** | Helpful copy + optional CTA; never confuse with loading | `JourneyEmptyState` |
| **Success** | Snackbar for async; inline only for form confirmation | existing snackbars |

### Spinner color

Always `SharedJourneyColors.MediterraneanTeal` (except inside buttons where default is OK).

### Empty vs partial empty

- **Truly empty** (zero items): `JourneyEmptyState` with icon + CTA.
- **Partial empty** (e.g. all groceries checked): muted inline `Text` or compact empty — not full card.

